name: CNN
text:
A 25-year-old Nevada man appears to be the first documented case of Covid-19 reinfection in the United States, researchers say.

Genetic tests indicate the patient was infected with two different varieties of the virus, the team reports. https://t.co/iJ5b0A0fFV
